<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring MVC</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是 </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">是</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">spring</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">中的</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#24292e">web</span></span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">开发模块，</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">一个基于</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> MVC </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">设计模式的轻量级</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Web </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">开发框架</span></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:disc">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">模型（</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Model</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，模型就是数据，就是</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> dao,bean</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">视图（</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">View</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，视图就是网页</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">,
                        JSP</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，用来展示模型中的数据</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">控制器（</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">C</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ontroller</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></strong></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，控制器的作用就是把不同的数据</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">(Model)</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，显示在不同的视图</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">(View)</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">上，</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Servlet
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">扮演的就是这样的角色</span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring MVC</span></strong>
        <strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">组件</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring MVC</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">主要由以下部分组成</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">前端控制器</span></strong></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:square">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">提供的前端控制器，是整个</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                        MVC</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的核心，</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                            style="color:#24292e">负责接收请求， 响应处理结果。</span></span></span></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">SpringMVC</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">所有的请求都通过它。</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Servlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">根据定义的具体规则拦截匹配的请求，分发到目标</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">来处理。 </span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring MVC</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">中，每个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">都持有一个自己的上下文对象</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">WebApplicationContext</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，它又继承了根（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">root</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">WebApplicationContext</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象中已经定义的所有</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Bean</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。这些继承的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Bean</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">可以在具体的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Servlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实例中被重载，在每个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Servlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实例中你也可以定义其作用域</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">(Scope)</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">下的新</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Bean</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">是框架的一个</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">Servlet</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">对象，父类是</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                    style="color:#24292e">HttpServlet</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#24292e">。 </span></span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">其主要工作有以下三项：</span></span>
        <ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
            <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">拦截获取符合特定格式的</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">URL</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">请求。</span></span>
            </li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">初始化</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">上下文对应</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">WebApplicationContext</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，并将其与业务层、持久化层的</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">WebApplicationContext</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">建立关联。</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">初始化</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                        MVC</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的各个组成组件，并装配到</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">中</span></span>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">将请求分发给</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring
                Controller</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">之前，需要借助于</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">提供的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">HandlerMapping</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">定位到具体的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">HandlerMapping</span></strong></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">控制器映射</span></strong></span></li>
    <li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">能够完成客户请求到</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">映射。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">后端控制器</span></strong></span>
        <ul style="list-style-type:square">
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">用于处理用户请求，处理完则返回</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ModelAndView</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象给</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">前端控制器，</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ModelAndView</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">中包含了模型（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Model</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）和视图（</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">View</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）。</span></span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">需要为并发用户处理上述请求，因此实现</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">接口时，必须保证线程安全并且可重用。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ModelAndView</span></strong></span></li>
    <li style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Http</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">请求过程中返回的模型（</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Model</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）和视图（</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">View</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ViewResolver</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">视图解析器</span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"></span></span><br></li>
</ul>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 40px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">提供的视图解析器（</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ViewResolver</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）在</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Web</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">应用中查找</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">View</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象，从而将相应结果渲染给客户</span></span><br></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>注</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是整个</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Web</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">应用的控制器；从微观考虑，</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是单个</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Http</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">请求处理过程中的控制器</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring MVC</span></strong>
        <strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">原理</span></strong></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">接收客户端发出的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Http</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">请求</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">控制器查询一个或多个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">HandlerMapping</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，找到处理请求的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">将请求提交到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">控制器。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Controller</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">调用业务逻辑处理后，返回</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ModelAndView</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">视图解析器。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">DispatcherServlet</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">查询一个或多个</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ViewResoler</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">视图解析器，找到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ModelAndView</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">指定的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">View</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">视图。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">View</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">视图负责将结果显示到客户端</span></span></li>
</ol>
